Certainly! Here’s a comprehensive, developer-friendly overview of the NMKR Studio API, tailored for integration into your Agno agent workflows. ￼

⸻

🔐 Authentication
	•	API Key: Obtain from your NMKR Studio account.
	•	Authorization Header: Include as a Bearer token in your request headers. ￼ ￼

Example: ￼

Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY



⸻

🌐 Base URLs
	•	Mainnet: https://studio-api.nmkr.io/v2/
	•	Testnet (Preprod): https://studio-api.preprod.nmkr.io/v2/ ￼

⸻

📁 Project Management
	•	Create Project: POST /v2/CreateProject
	•	List Projects: GET /v2/ListProjects
	•	Get Project Details: GET /v2/ProjectDetails/{projectUid}
	•	Delete Project: DELETE /v2/DeleteProject/{projectUid}

⸻

🖼️ Asset (NFT) Management
	•	Upload NFT: POST /v2/UploadNft/{projectUid}
	•	Get NFT Details by ID: GET /v2/GetNftDetailsById/{nftUid}
	•	Get NFT Details by Token Name: GET /v2/GetNftDetailsByTokenname/{projectUid}/{nftName}
	•	Update Metadata: PUT /v2/UpdateMetadata/{projectUid}/{nftUid}
	•	Delete NFT: DELETE /v2/DeleteNft/{nftUid} ￼

⸻

🪙 Minting
	•	Mint and Send Random NFT: GET /v2/MintAndSendRandom/{projectUid}/{count}/{walletAddress}
	•	Mint and Send Specific NFT: GET /v2/MintAndSendSpecific/{projectUid}/{nftUid}/{count}/{walletAddress} ￼

⸻

💳 Payment Transactions
	•	Create Payment Transaction: POST /v2/CreatePaymentTransaction
	•	Get Payment Transaction State: GET /v2/ProceedPaymentTransaction/{paymentTransactionUid}/GetTransactionState
	•	Get Payment Address: GET /v2/ProceedPaymentTransaction/{paymentTransactionUid}/PaymentAddress
	•	Submit Transaction: POST /v2/ProceedPaymentTransaction/{paymentTransactionUid}/SubmitTransaction
	•	Cancel Transaction: POST /v2/ProceedPaymentTransaction/{paymentTransactionUid}/CancelTransaction ￼ ￼

⸻

🛠️ Tools & Utilities
	•	Managed Wallets: Manage wallets within NMKR Studio.
	•	Split Addresses: Handle revenue splits among multiple addresses.
	•	Direct Sales: Set up direct NFT sales.
	•	Policy Snapshot: Retrieve snapshots of policy states. ￼ ￼

